c: 17
v: 33
t: "Nize ningabulali nabani na okubulawa kwakhe uAllâh Akwaleleyo, ngaphandle kwesizathu esisebulungiseni. Ke kaloku nabani na obulewe ngendlela engalunganga, Thina Sinike indlalifa yakhe igunya lokuba inkqange umthetho wokulingana ngesohlwayo okanye ixolele, ithabathe idiyah5. Kodwa ke (indlalifa leyo) mayingatsibi imida ebekiweyo kumbandela wokuthabatha ubomi. Ngokwenene yona incedisiwe (ngumthetho)"